| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1951 — Recovery Inhibition (darkvault)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0936d5f0-456e-58b3-a05d-8ad51c3d1b63"
